  "slug": "tapping-for-conflict-avoidance",
  "title": "Tapping for conflict avoidance",
  "subtitle": "A five-minute tapping sequence for the fawn response in disagreements",
  "excerpt": "A five-minute tapping sequence for the automatic people-pleasing that kicks in when a disagreement starts. For when you agree, go quiet, or change the subject to avoid conflict.",
  "type": "PRACTICE",
  "categorySlug": "mindset",
