  "body": {
    "type": "doc",
    "content": [
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Conflict avoidance is a survival strategy. At some point, keeping the peace was the safest option. This tapping sequence works with that history rather than against it."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {"level": 2},
        "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Setup"}]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Tap the karate chop point on the side of your hand and repeat three times:"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "bulletList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Even though I go quiet when things get difficult, I accept myself and how I learned to cope."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Even though part of me changes shape to avoid disagreement, I am willing to understand where that comes from."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Even though I sometimes agree when I don't mean it, I accept myself and this habit."}]}]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {"level": 2},
        "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Round one: name it"}]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Tap through the points (eyebrow, side of eye, under eye, under nose, chin, collarbone, under arm, top of head) while saying:"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "bulletList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "This pull to agree."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "This need for the discomfort to stop."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "The way I disappear into agreeableness."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "The fear underneath the yes."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "The cost of swallowing what I actually think."}]}]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {"level": 2},
        "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Round two: shift"}]
      },
      {
        "type": "bulletList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "I learned to keep the peace because it worked."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "That was a good strategy at the time."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "I am allowed to have a view."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "A different view does not end the relationship."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "I can disagree and still be loved."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "My voice is allowed in this."}]}]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {"level": 2},
        "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Where this practice comes from"}]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Original to homemade.education."
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  }
}
